<p><font size="4"><tt>Kitty Rehberg <br>
2279 310th Street <br>
Rowley, IA 52329 <br>
319-938-2659 <br>
Iowa Senate District 14 <br>
Republican Challenger </tt></font></p>

<ol>
    <li><font size="4"><tt>Do you think we are winning the War on Drugs? </tt></font><blockquote>
