<p><font size="4"><tt>Albert Schoeman <br>
1111 Bauch St. <br>
Waterloo, IA 50701 <br>
319-234-1020 <br>
U.S. House District 2 <br>
Libertarian Challenger </tt></font></p>

<ol>
