<title>Construction Signs Suck</title>

<p>You know how when a dad catches a kid smoking, and as punishment makes
the kid smoke the whole pack/carton? The point here is that after a while, the kid gets to really hate smoking. Some people need a little extra help...<p>

Which is why I created The "Construction Signs Suck" Page. If enough of those stupid little black and yellow man-in-hat-with-a-shovel graphics are in the same place, it might just make people realise how annoying they are.<br>
If this page helps save just one persons' sanity, then that is some good, at least.
<p><hr><p>

<a href= "http://www.moscow.com/images/Icons/buttons-3d-border/smallat_work_btn.gif"><IMG border=0 width=20 height=20 alt="*" SRC= "http://www.moscow.com/images/Icons/buttons-3d-border/smallat_work_btn.gif"></A>

<a href="http://www.ermis.forthnet.gr/icons/underc.gif"><img border=0 width=30 height=30 alt="*" src="http://www.ermis.forthnet.gr/icons/underc.gif"></a>

<a href="http://call.army.mil:1100/call/gifs/images/undercon.gif"><img border=0 width=43 height=34 alt="*" src="http://call.army.mil:1100/call/gifs/images/undercon.gif"></a>

<a href="http://www.emsl.pnl.gov:2080/images/cie/icons/construction6.gif"><img border=0 width=40 height=40 alt="*" src="http://www.emsl.pnl.gov:2080/images/cie/icons/construction6.gif"></a>

