<hr>              IN THE UNITED STATES COURT OF APPEALS
               FOR THE DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA CIRCUIT
_________________________________________________________________

                           No. 94-1605
_________________________________________________________________


                         CARL ERIC OLSEN

                           Petitioner,

                               v.

                 DRUG ENFORCEMENT ADMINISTRATION

                           Respondent.

