<title>H.R. 4498 - therapeutic use of marihuana</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" link="#0000FF"
vlink="#800080" alink="#FF0000">

<blockquote>
    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
            <td width="140"><center><strong>97</strong><font
            size="2"><strong>TH</strong></font><strong> CONGRESS<br>
            2</strong><font size="2"><strong>D SESSION</strong></font></center>
