            <td><font size="7"><strong>H.R.
            4498</strong></font>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <p><font size="3">To provide for the therapeutic use of
    marihuana in situations involving life-<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;threatening or
    sense-threatening illnesses and to provide adequate supplies
    of<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;marihuana for such use.</font></p>
