<body bgcolor="000000" text="FFFFFF" link="00FF66" vlink="00FFFF"
alink="FF3300">
<center>

<h4>UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE<br>
Drug Enforcement Administration<br>
In The Matter Of<br>
MARIJUANA RESCHEDULING PETITION<br>
Docket No. 86-22<br>
OPINION AND RECOMMENDED RULING, FINDINGS OF<br>
FACT, CONCLUSIONS OF LAW AND DECISION OF<br>
ADMINISTRATIVE LAW JUDGE<br>
FRANCIS L. YOUNG, Administrative Law Judge<br>
DATED: SEPTEMBER 6, 1988</h4>
</center>


<h4><img src="../../images/reddot.gif"> <a href="young1.html">Judge
Young's ruling (Pages 1-15)</a> </h4>

