<DOCHDR>
http://www.commonlink.com:80/users/carl-olsen/MEDICAL/jenks.html 204.77.198.71 19970106043624 text/html 18006
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.5 ID/11095
Message-ID: <aef5ecaf.7053@www.commonlink.com>
Date: Sunday, 05-Jan-97 23:41:35 GMT
Last-Modified: Saturday, 07-Dec-96 21:34:41 GMT
Content-type: text/html
