86-22, Opinion, Recommended Ruling, Findings of Fact, Conclusions
of Law, and Decision of Administrative Law Judge, September 6,
1988. Washington, DC: Drug Enforcement Agency; 1988.</h5>

<h5>2. Grinspoon L., Bakalar J. Marihuana, the Forbidden
Medicine. New Haven, Conn.: Yale University Press; 1993.</h5>

<h5>3. In the Matter of Marijuana Rescheduling Petition, Docket
86-22, Affidavit of Daniel Daneac, M.D. Washington, DC: Drug
Enforcement Agency; 1987.</h5>

<h5>4. Doblin R., Kleiman M.A.R. Marihuana as anti-emetic
medicine: a survey of oncologists' attitudes and experiences. J
Clin Oncol, 1991;9:1275-1290. </h5>

<hr>

<h4>1876 JAMA, June 21, 1995 -- Vol. 273, No. 23</h4>

