<CENTER>(iii)</CENTER></PRE><HR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=3>IN THE</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>SUPREME COURT OF THE UNITED STATES</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE=3>OCTOBER TERM, 1995</FONT></CENTER><P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=3>No: __________</FONT></CENTER><P>
<FONT SIZE=3><CENTER>JOHN M. GRUBOR,</CENTER>
<CENTER>Petitioner,</CENTER><P>

<CENTER>vs.</CENTER><P>

<CENTER>THE COMMONWEALTH OF PENNSYLVANIA<BR>
DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION<BR>
