<DOCHDR>
http://www.commonlink.com:80/users/carl-olsen/RELIGION/boyll.html 204.77.198.71 19970106044917 text/html 42573
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.5 ID/11095
Message-ID: <aef5efa9.7123@www.commonlink.com>
Date: Sunday, 05-Jan-97 23:54:17 GMT
