<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type"
content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 2.0">
<title>Legislators who are unsure about marijuana for medical use</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<p align="center"><font size="3" face="Arial"><strong>LEGISLATORS
WHO ARE UNSURE ABOUT CHANGES IN THE LAW<br>
TO PREVENT THE ARREST AND PROSECUTION<br>
OF MEDICAL MARIJUANA USERS</strong></font></p>

<p align="center"><font size="3" face="Arial"><strong>REPUBLICANS</strong></font></p>
<div align="center"><center>

