<p><b>___________________________________________________________________________</b> <SPACER TYPE="VERTICAL" SIZE="10"> <SPACER TYPE="HORIZONTAL" SIZE="10">236
National Drive<SPACER TYPE="HORIZONTAL" SIZE="10"><b>-<SPACER TYPE="HORIZONTAL" SIZE="10"></b>Waterloo, Iowa 50701<SPACER TYPE="HORIZONTAL" SIZE="10"><b>-<SPACER TYPE="HORIZONTAL" SIZE="10"></b>(319) 234-0109 <SPACER TYPE="VERTICAL" SIZE="5"> </p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="75%">
    <tr>
        <td><p align="center">W. H. Verduyn, M.D. <br>
        <font size="2">Medical Director <br>
        Physical Medicine &amp; <br>
