          Vol. XII   -  Cross Examination, February 2, 1988 

          Vol. XIII  -  Cross Examination, February 4, 1988 

          Vol. XIV   -  Cross Examination, February 5, 1988 

          Vol. XV    -  Oral Argument, June 10, 1988 

